      "span_text": "Methods for determining relative cell volume have been described previously. 40 An inverted microscope (Diaphot, Nikon, Inc) equipped with Hoffman modulation optics (ϫ40; numerical aperture, 0.55) and a high-resolution TV camera (CCD72, Dage-MTI) coupled to a video frame-grabber (Targa-M8, Truevision) was used to image myocytes."
